metadata.description: The 456 Collector's Club by Zevi G. is a collection of 4560 unique NFTs. The 456 mint pass is designed specifically to give early supporters higher access to this collection. One mint pass is equivalent to 5 NFTs from the collection. Each wallet is allowed to purchase up to 5 mint passes. On public mint day, each pass will be allowed to mint 5 NFTs at no additional cost, aside from gas fees for the transaction.
metadata.name: 456 Mint Pass #1
